uce%20on%20the%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Roopa%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20the%20guests%E2%80%99%20favourites%20are%20the%20%3Cem%3Eappam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Estew%2C%20puttu%2C%20kadala%2C%20dosa%2C%20sambar%2C%20idiyappam%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20chicken%20curry.%20And%20no%20one%20is%20allowed%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20city%20without%20Praveen%E2%80%99s%20(head%20chef)%20special%20dal%20%3Cem%3Etadka%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Eshahi%20tukda%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Hire%20The%20Right%20People%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHiring%20the%20right%20people%20to%20help%20you%20successfully%20run%20the%20homestay%20is%20another%20important%20lesson%20that%20most%20of%20these%20owners%20share.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20with%20my%20homestay%2C%20Ludhramani%20Bhaiya%2C%20who%20is%20now%20our%20cook%2C%20became%20my%20backbone.%20He%20helped%20me%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Heena.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20he%20helps%20me%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20place%20and%20he%20also%20is%20our%20cook.%20He%20makes%20delicious%20authentic%20Himachali%20food%20at%20our%20homestay%20which%20leaves%20all%20our%20guests%20happy%20and%20satisfied%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%C2%A0%20Always%20Be%20Eager%20To%20Learn%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%2089-year-old%20Laxmi%20Ammal%20studied%20only%20till%20Class%203%2C%20and%2071-year-old%20Kasthuri%20Sivaraman%20completed%20Class%207%20in%20a%20Tamil-medium%20school%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282423%2Ftamil-nadu-best-farm-stay-grandma-nature-organic-food-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20a%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20something%20these%20women%20would%20have%20never%20imagined%20as%20young%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cf