cience%2C%20art%2C%20computers%20and%20theatre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20astounding%20than%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20participation%20has%20been%20the%20support%20of%20the%20parents%2C%20notes%20Seema.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20begun%20to%20see%20an%20improvement%20in%20their%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20realisation%20deepened%20during%20the%20lockdown%20that%20ensued%20amid%20the%20COVID%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20online%20classes%2C%20it%20so%20happened%20that%20parents%20were%20at%20home%20while%20the%20kids%20were%20learning.%20We%20would%20send%20them%20activities%20and%20worksheets%20to%20solve.%20The%20parents%20ended%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334571%2Fkalpit-veerwal-jee-main-topper-launches-education-startup-iit-bombay-placement-package%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elearning%20a%20lot%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20bargain%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20chuckles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20lockdown%2C%20the%20entire%20%3Cem%3Ebasti%3C%2Fem%3E%20knew%20the%20days%20of%20the%20week%2C%20months%20of%20the%20year%2C%20and%20multiplication%20tables%20on%20the%20tips%20of%20their%20fingers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20parents%20got%20to%20see%20how%20much%20value%20we%20are%20adding%20to%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20lives.%20They%20realised%20that%20their%20children%20actually%20study%20at%20Nayi%20Disha%20and%20that%20there%20are%20people%20who%20are%20spending%20dedicated%20time%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20change%20in%20mindset%20is%20refreshing.%20The%20parents%E2%80%99%20new%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334155%2Fbengaluru-ngo-dream-a-dream-educates-underprivileged-children-life-skills-happiness-curriculum-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eview%20of%20the%20NGO%3C%2Fa%3