%20about%20what%20happens%20to%20flower%20waste%20at%20temples.%20An%20International%20Journal%20for%20Research%20in%20Applied%20Science%20%26amp%3B%20Engineering%20Technology%20report%20states%20that%20every%20year%2C%20approximately%20eight%20million%20tonnes%20of%20waste%20flowers%20are%20dumped%20in%C2%A0Indian%20rivers.%20Poonam%20adds%20that%20floral%20waste%20reportedly%20accounts%20for%2016%20percent%20of%20the%20river%20pollutants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20had%20found%20her%20calling%20and%20set%20out%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20floral%20waste.%20In%20June%202019%2C%20she%20set%20up%20Aaruhi%20Enterprises%20with%20her%20friend%20Pinki%20Yadav%2C%20and%20started%20making%20incense%20sticks%2C%20dhoop%20sticks%2C%20diyas%2C%20idols%20and%20more%2C%20using%20floral%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20month%2C%20her%20venture%20recycles%201%2C000%20kg%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339831%2Fjamshedpur-rajiv-sharma-alve-smart-air-fresheners-plastic-free-eco-friendly-temple-flower-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efloral%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20earns%20more%20than%20Rs%202%20lakh.%20The%20entrepreneur%2C%20now%2041%2C%20has%20also%20provided%20training%20to%20over%203%2C000%20women%20on%20making%20these%20products%20using%20floral%20waste%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20waste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20venture%20started%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam5-1709639330.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Poonam%20started%20recycling%20floral%20waste%20in%20June%202019%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpo